-- Switzerland's Kuoni Sees Growth of Up to 20% in India, China, Finanz Says
-- B y   C a r o l y n   B a n d e l
-- 2010-09-21T16:35:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/switzerland-s-kuoni-sees-growth-of-up-to-20-in-india-china-finanz-says.html
Kuoni Reisen Holding AG  expects
growth in India and China to be between 10 percent and 20
percent, outgoing Chief Financial Officer  Max Katz  said in an
interview with Finanz und Wirtschaft.  Growth in Europe may be between 1 percent and 2 percent,
Katz told the Zurich-based newspaper in an e-mailed pre-release
of an interview that will be published tomorrow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Carolyn Bandel  in Zurich at 
 cbandel@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at   fconnelly@bloomberg.net  